Iterate over each folder in @"720sync" with name starting "Arya_Flat_" 
In each such folder, find the video named like @"repn_flat_arya_full_720p.mp4", (where n is some integer).
The video consists of two camera views to cover the dog's range of motion from right to left, and we need to focus only on the right camera view for this task since the dog's motion starts from the right. 
The dog is stationary for a period of time at the beginning of the video, followed by the first onset of motion. We need to find the frame number where the pose of the dog is just starting its first stride. 
